  "title": "Corporate Secretarial Associate",
  "description": "<p>Company: Cypress Singapore PAC</p><p>Cypress Policy of Trust & Empowerment allows flexible\nworking arrangements that allows lifestyle choices and managing childcare or\neldercare needs. Workloads will be allocated taking into consideration of each\ncandidates’ situation.</p><p>Job Title: Corporate Secretarial Associate</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for a highly motivated individual with proven\ntrack record of Corporate Secretarial experiences to join our team of Corporate\nSecretarial Professionals</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>You will be assisting the Assistant Manager in corporate\nsecretarial and admin work, which includes:</p><p>° Preparation of Directors’ and Shareholders’ Resolutions\nand Statutory Returns</p><p>° Prepare accounts in XBRL & submission</p><p>° Ensure compliance with statutory and regulatory\nrequirements (including deadlines)</p><p>° Handle all statutory filings with ACRA, MOM, IRAS and\nother regional/local government bodies</p><p>° General administration work, including filing and\narranging appointments</p><p>° Maintain a good working relationship with clients and\nmanage their expectations</p><p>° Other ad-hoc duties as and when required</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>° Bachelor's in Accounting or Law or equivalent</p><p>° At least 3 years of relevant experience in a professional\nfirm</p><p>° Strong interpersonal, communication and written skills</p><p>° An eye for detail and deadline-oriented</p><p>° Able to work independently</p><p>° Accountability, a proactive approach, and a positive work\nattitude.</p>",
